            <h2>Why sewer backups require immediate action</h2>
            <p>Sewer backups are more than an inconvenience — they create real health risks and escalating property damage.</p>
            <ul class="check-list">
              <li>Raw sewage contains bacteria, viruses, and parasites that cause serious illness</li>
